*Mojoj* kući je potrebna nova krovna konstrukcija. (My house needs a new roof construction.)

*Mojoj* majci su uvek bile važne porodične veze. (My mother has always valued family ties.)

*Mojoj* sestri je ovaj film bio veoma zanimljiv. (My sister found this movie very interesting.)

*Mojoj* susedi je potrebna pomoć u sadnji cveća. (My neighbour needs help planting flowers.)

*Mojoj* školi je potrebno obnoviti fasadu. (My school needs to renovate its facade.)